name: Strawberry Graham Cracker Bites
author: kellybean
summary: I decided to try this recipe in preparation for the Fourth of July. It is an easy-to-make, simple recipe that is great for social gatherings, parties, and Fourth of July celebrations.
ingredients: 1 (13 ounce) jar chocolate-hazelnut spread (such as Nutella®)
directions: Cut the bottoms of each strawberry so they can stand upright on a plate; hollow out the top of each strawberry
Spoon whipped cream and chocolate-hazelnut spread into the hollow part of each strawberry; top with 1 blueberry
Cover each filled strawberry with a mini graham cracker
